    "created_at": "2015-08-29T16:16:42Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-08-29T16:16:42Z",
    "body": "The issue with graceful-fs not working on io.js was resolved a couple of months ago, so it should work with Electron.\nIf you try to open lots of files together, but you let them close once you read them, then graceful-fs could solve the issue for you. If you need to keep all of them open at the same time, then it won't work for you. You could also just test it and see if it solves the issue for you.\n\nIn any case it seems that @deepak1556, is adding an API to change the limit.\n"
